title: Sherlock | S01-S04E00 | 1080p Bluray Rip | HEVC x265 | AC-3/FLAC
description:
Sources: Retail blu-ray (S01-2), http://hdclub.org/details.php?id=18509 (S03), https://rarbg.to/torrent/srycz12 (S04E00)
Method: MakeMKV to remux & decode DTS-HDMA/TrueHD, audio processed with lossywav, video encoded with x265, muxed with Mkvtoolnix

Video encode settings:

x265 preset 'Slower', CRF 23, 10-bit colour, with further settings "--ipratio 1.1 --pbratio 1.1 --aq-mode 3 --aq-strength k --psy-rd 2 --rdoq-level 0 --psy-rdoq 0 --qcomp 0.8"
--aq-strength: For S01E00, S02E02 & S03E03, k=0.2; for S04E00, k=1.0; otherwise, k=0.6

Notes:

S01-2 audio copied, S03 & S04E00 audio processed with lossyWAV at quality 'high'; FLAC encoding with eac3to
Audio is 5.1 apart from S01E00 (stereo) and S04E00 (7.1)
Commentary tracks included in episodes S01E01, S01E03, S02E01 & S02E02 (192 Kbps stereo AC-3) with various contributors
English subtitles have been converted to text-based format with SubExtractor
Episode names included in titles, but for clarification, S01E00 is the unaired pilot, and S04E00 is 'The Abominable Bride'
